      <title>小程序中的相对路径与绝对路径</title>
      <link href="/2019/12/01/%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84/"/>
      <url>/2019/12/01/%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>小程序中有相对路径和绝对路径的区别</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ssuiw97/PicBedForHexoBlog/master/img/miniProgram/reading%20notes/mp3-1.jpg" alt="加入图片后的文件结构"></p><ol><li>绝对路径</li></ol><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">image</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"/images/avatar/avatar-1.png"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>以“/”开头，“/”代表根目录</li></ul><ol start="2"><li>相对路径</li></ol><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">image</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"../../images/avatar/avatar-1.png"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>“..”代表向上一级</li></ul><blockquote><p>这里使用绝对路径更加简洁</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
