    <entry>
      <title>不要在template上注册事件</title>
      <link href="/2019/11/29/%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%A8template%E4%B8%8A%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6/"/>
      <url>/2019/11/29/%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%A8template%E4%B8%8A%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在template上注册事件是无效的。template标签仅仅是一个占位符，在编译后会被template模板内容替换。</p><blockquote><p>同样，也不能在block标签上注册事件，因为block也会在编译后消失。</p></blockquote><p>解决方法：增加view容器包裹template模板</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">block</span> <span class="attr">wx:for</span>=<span class="string">"&#123;&#123;postList&#125;&#125;"</span> <span class="attr">wx:for-item</span>=<span class="string">"item"</span><span class="attr">item</span> <span class="attr">wx:for-index</span>=<span class="string">"idx"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span> <span class="attr">catchtap</span>=<span class="string">"onTapToDetail"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">template</span> <span class="attr">is</span>=<span class="string">"postItemTpl"</span> <span class="attr">data</span>=<span class="string">"...item"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">block</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
